    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45456</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_178_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はぐはぐはぐ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Omnomnomnomnom</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45528</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_178_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ホント、よく食うよな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whoa, you sure can eat.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45612</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_178_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だって、おなか空いてるんだもん</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well, I'm hungry okay?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45700</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_178_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>成長期だし、好き嫌いなく食べないとね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Given that she's a growing child, she cannot
afford to be picky.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45820</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_178_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;みたいにあれも嫌い、
これも嫌いって言ってたら大きくなれないよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>She doesn't want to be like you, &lt;Dio&gt;, you always pick
at your food. You'll never grow at this rate.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45952</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_178_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>その割に&lt;Mel&gt;なんて、出るところ出ないで、
出なくていいとこ、出てんじゃねーか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That might be the case, but even then &lt;Mel&gt; won't grow
at the places she wants to grow anyway.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46040</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_178_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……うぉおっ！！
お、おまえ……！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>U-Uwaagh!! Y-You!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46232</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_178_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ほんと、お約束だね～、&lt;Dio&gt;くん。
今のわざとでしょ？　ね？　わざと？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're really sticking to your promise, &lt;Dio&gt;~
You really meant that, didn't you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes>need context</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
